Title: Relates to the disposal of seized perishable or canned foods
Summary: Relates to the disposal of seized perishable or canned foods; such foods should not be disposed of but should be donated to a food relief organization or homeless shelter.
LawCode: Amd ยง20-468, NYC Ad Cd
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the administrative code of the city of New York, in relation to the disposal of seized perishable or canned foods
